
======================================================================
CRYPTO-001 Mining pool connection [CRITICAL]
======================================================================

Category:
  Cryptomining  (detector: rules)

Description:
  Connection to cryptocurrency mining pools

Recommendation:
  Remove cryptomining components

CWE: CWE-506

Technical Details:
  Mining pools use the stratum protocol (stratum+tcp://) for work
  distribution. Presence of pool URLs indicates unauthorized mining.

======================================================================
